#魔卡少女樱[超话]##cos正片##魔卡少女樱cos##木之本樱##百变小樱##小樱##樱狼##clamp##萌系小姐姐##木之本樱0401生日快乐##cos神还原#

小樱:@綠月團長喵
摄影:@爱瑟loki
后期:@囚人笑君 吹爆太太
场地: @幻象剧场-Phantom_Theatre
服装:松果
妆娘:@coserwan
文案: @綠月團長喵
文案翻译:小风

The sand is held up in both hands, but it slips away through the fingers.
The sun filters through leafy trees onto the ground of forest, just like the sunshine dances.
The little brook flows, without a stop for rest.
The hourglass continues to roll over and over on the desk.
Has the fairy flapped her wings for 365 times already?
Blossoms and withers the flowers. Comes and goes four seasons.
